      • QuadrupleGUIImageSheet

        public QuadrupleGUIImageSheet​(BoundedImageSheet def,
                              BoundedImageSheet rollOver,
                              BoundedImageSheet pressed,
                              BoundedImageSheet disabled)
        Creates a new image sheet collection for GUI applications.
        Parameters:
        def - The default image sheet used for no interaction with the button.
        rollOver - The image sheet used for when the mouse is over the button, but not pressed.
        pressed - The image sheet used for when the button is pressed.
        disabled - The image sheet used for when the button is disabled.
